{
  "texts": [
    "Their study concluded that EML1 is the best location for an orbiting depot.",
    "The design reference missions are commercial satellite servicing mission (CSS), Mars cargo mission (MC), and propellant delivery mission.",
    "△V requirements and time-of-flight calculations are presented based on two-body orbital mechanics.",
    "Depot locations are LEO, GEO, and EML1.",
    "The boil-off consideration requires knowledge of the heat fluxes at different locations."
  ]
}